videos.description: Eleanna Christinaki knocks down two 3-pointers early as the Terps lead Ohio State.
videos.headline: Maryland's Christinaki sinks back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Sierra Calhoun hits a 3-pointer off of a step-back crossover.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Calhoun knocks down step-back 3

videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell passes Maya Moore for 9th all-time on the NCAA scoring list with a layup in the first quarter against Maryland.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Mitchell passes Moore on all-time scoring list

videos.description: Kaila Charles creates a 3-point play late in the 2nd quarter to extend the Terp's lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: Maryland's Charles draws foul, hits layup
